{"tid":804023,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾意食crepe?","createTime":"2018-09-02T16:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T01:35:25.000Z","uid":175988,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40d55b944817dec2cf8ddfd8ce6a4bf52b47e15b","tid":804023,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"橙酒crepe真係無敵，不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行街見到有間舖專賣法式薄餅，就入去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>La Creperie @ 灣仔</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/A5iQ01K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA5iQ01K.jpg&h=75627b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cvwIl0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcvwIl0Y.jpg&h=22fe65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>煙熏火腿芝士雞蛋/焦糖蘋果薄餅</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n薄餅邊位夠脆，中心韌度適中，帶小麥同蛋嘅香氣<br />\n<br />\n蘋果粒腍滑中帶爽脆，唔會過甜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n餅皮有陣燶味，食落帶苦<br />\n<br />\n䶢薄餅配搭失衡，火腿同芝士一齊食䶢上加䶢，完撚全cover哂所有食材味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n性價比幾低，䶢薄餅全部配料係現成食材都要百幾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 普普通通，齋叫甜crepe會好啲</strong>"},{"pid":"ed66152bb93020fdd13b05abe1085d3f398734be","tid":804023,"uid":197797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"見佢有團購打算試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b5bc8a6718ac93ec5148dd13e0a0dc65812294","tid":804023,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T01:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}